  "title": "Warehouse Assistant // Jurong East // Attractive Salary Package //  Bonus",
  "description": "<p><strong>🌟Position: Warehouse Assistant </strong><br />⏰Working Time: 9am - 6pm (Mon - Fri); 9am - 1pm (Sat)<br />📍Work Location: Toh Guan Rd (Near Jurong East)<br /><strong>💵</strong>Basic Salary: up to $2600 <em><strong>(subject to experience)</strong></em> + OT + Bonus</p><p><br /><strong>Job scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Handle inbound & outbound orders</li><li>Update the inventory and transaction in WMS system </li><li>Use Excel for basic reporting & tracking </li><li>Operate MHE (pallet jack / stacker / forklift)</li><li>Load & unloading cargo up to 20kg</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>Familiar with WMS & basic excel</li><li>Able to lift up to 20kg</li><li>Experience with MHE preferred</li></ul><p><br />EA License No: 20C0137<br />EA Personnel No: R1988305<br />EA Personnel Name: CHI YAN</p>",
